## [2.0.0] - 2024-12-24

### üéØ Major Changes - Economy System Separation
- **BREAKING**: Removed all economy and casino features from main bot
- Moved economy system to separate bot in \`another-bot/\` folder
- Removed SQLAlchemy dependency from main bot
- Simplified bot architecture for community-focused features

### ‚ú® Added
- **Ticket System**: Complete support ticket management with Discord threads
  - Multiple ticket categories (Support, Bug Reports, Partnership, etc.)
  - Persistent ticket panels with button interface
  - Ticket claiming and closing functionality
  - Customizable support team roles
  - Ticket logging channel support
  - Auto-incrementing ticket numbers
- **Database Module**: Created \`utils/database.py\` for centralized database configuration
- **Admin Commands**: New general admin commands (reload, sync)

### üóëÔ∏è Removed (Moved to another-bot/)
- **Economy Cog**: All economy commands (balance, work, daily, weekly, etc.)
- **Casino Cog**: All casino games (blackjack, roulette, slots, etc.)
- **Economy Models**: User, Wallet, Transaction, Bet models
- **Economy Utils**: economy_utils.py, anti_fraud.py
- **Economy Admin Commands**: add_money, reset_economy (moved to admin_economy.py)
- **Economy Configuration**: Removed economy settings from main config

### üîÑ Changed
- **Admin Cog**: Replaced with lightweight admin cog (reload, sync commands only)
- **Help System**: Removed economy/casino references
- **Bot Description**: Updated to focus on community engagement and support
- **README.md**: Completely rewritten to reflect new bot focus
- **Configuration**: Removed database_url and economy settings from main config

### üìù Documentation
- Created \`another-bot/README.md\` - Setup guide for economy bot
- Created \`another-bot/MIGRATION_SUMMARY.md\` - Detailed migration documentation
- Created \`another-bot/config.py\` - Standalone economy bot configuration
- Updated main README with new feature set and ticket system documentation

### üêõ Fixed
- Fixed missing \`create_info_embed\` function in utils/helpers.py
- Fixed import errors in tickets.py
- Fixed database configuration issues

